cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.HC 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language understanding and machine translation. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of machine learning techniques to improve NLU performance. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper involves training a large-scale NLU system using machine learning methods. 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is a possible category as the paper discusses methods for reducing manual effort in data collection and improving NLU performance. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is also a possible category as the paper deals with voice-controlled devices and improving user experience through better NLU performance.
